{"tid":1647732,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"每次都話少人，明明就係宣傳不足","createTime":"2019-10-12T01:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T02:14:22.000Z","uid":285794,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8f511e28c0450e09b4afac0b4f4bab5eba333f93","tid":1647732,"uid":285794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T01:23:46.000Z","msg":"P牌仔一個，啱聽就聽啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6月既時候，早一、兩個禮拜已經講緊禮拜亦六、日有咩做<br />\n依家你問我下個禮拜六、日有咩做<br />\n我都唔一定答到你<br />\n仲要玩即慶吹雞18區<br />\n<br />\n其實無大台玩即慶真係唔得<br />\n因為一定要有共識先有行動<br />\n時間越多越有共識，自然人就會多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以講咗好耐&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n唔好浪費太多時間、空間推無用既資訊<br />\n連登熱門就係得咁多位<br />\n仲要依家有五毛瘋狂吹風<br />\n有時間笑黑警、政府、中共<br />\n<br />\n不如專心推行動post、戰術post<br />\n無哂d主線、教學，點玩香城online呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"b65b5d0fd9b114e0a8fa97375ea59490ba924829","tid":1647732,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T01:27:17.000Z","msg":"對上一次淡左，咪又係全世界掛住做神探囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51cf17b5ec1e51c5e7fb69d7e16beb01b89f88ca","tid":1647732,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T01:36:41.000Z","msg":"今日最新風向：分化香港人同美國之間嘅關係<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1647718\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1647718</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1138f23910d2400866348f83371e7164bf65702d","tid":1647732,"uid":196087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T01:53:39.000Z","msg":"Agger 同埋咪撚一日排幾個活動，點推呀"},{"pid":"56795deca7d4c5b3d0a4c3a39e356bc1edaca5c5","tid":1647732,"uid":188261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T01:56:03.000Z","msg":"超級認同 成個熱門都冇一個正姐post 來來去去都係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">神探同風向post</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7f19784ed8c92f5a8d129be9